Name:           python-pynamodb
Version:        4.3.3
Release:        0
Summary:        Python Interface to DynamoDB
License:        MIT
URL:            https://github.com/pynamodb/PynamoDB
Source0:        https://files.pythonhosted.org/packages/source/p/pynamodb/pynamodb-%{version}.tar.gz
